@DATABASE "Scumball"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Superkid In Space"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                             Superkid In Space
                             =================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Eveything = x  " rxs "address command zxampoke(51695,255)"}         51695,x (x= 1-255)
@{"No Guards/Balls" rxs "address command zxampoke(46790,0"}         46790,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
